‚óŹ The fix replaces the HashMap<OpHandle, (Instant, bool)> in-flight tracking
  with a VecDeque<(Instant, bool)> FIFO queue. The worker can't predict
  actor-assigned OpHandle values, so instead it tracks submissions in order and
  pops completions from the front regardless of handle.

